name: Ledblinker
tagline: Test application on qt 5.5 for Raspberry Pi
body:
# LEDBlinker

This project is my attempt to create GUI application which manages the frequency and duty cycle of LED blinking;

LED is connected to GPIO_0. 
The purpose of this project is to get working code which can be reused to control multicolor LED.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
